                },
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When the gold defender is destroyed, it melts into worthless slag. As it melts, it releases a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] cloud of fumes and a 10-foot radius puddle of molten metal. Creatures that breathe fumes are exposed to gold defender poison. Creatures that move through the puddle take [[/r 10d6[fire]]] damage. The fumes dissipate after 1 round and the puddle cools after 1 minute.</p>"
                },
