        {
            "_id": "EGB2VKnTeg8RQSML",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
            "name": "Inexorable March",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionCategory": {
                    "value": "offensive"
                },
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The gold defender Strides up to its Speed, pushing back each creature whose space it moves into and damaging them if they try to stop its movement. A creature can attempt to bar the way by succeeding at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:37|name:Block Golem Movement] save. On a critical success, the resisting creature takes no damage; otherwise, it is damaged as if hit by the defender's fist Strike.</p>"
                },
